[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0126","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0126.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0462","title":"Linux Perl suidperl 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Linux Perl 中的 suidperl 组件在解析 setuid 脚本时未检查文件系统的 nosuid 挂载选项，本地攻击者可将特制 setuid Perl 脚本放置于可挂载文件系统（如 CD-ROM 或软盘）上，通过诱使目标系统挂载并执行该脚本触发漏洞。成功利用后可获取 root 权限执行任意代码，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 SUSE Linux 等多个发行版，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0462"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:26.813","remediation":"升级 Perl 至 5.004_04 或更高版本，该版本已修复 suidperl 对 nosuid 挂载选项的检查逻辑。作为临时缓解措施，执行 `chmod u-s /usr/bin/suidperl` 移除 suidperl 的 setuid 权限位，并将所有可移动文件系统（如 CD-ROM、软盘）以 `nosuid` 选项挂载，防止攻击者通过可移动介质提权至 root。长期建议迁移至 suidperl 已被彻底移除的 Perl 5.26+ 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/339"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0126.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0074","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0074.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0422","title":"NetBSD mount noexec 标志绕过漏洞","description":"NetBSD 1.3.3 的 mount 命令存在安全绕过漏洞，本地攻击者可通过挂载特定的文件系统绕过 \"noexec\" 标志限制，在标记为禁止执行的文件系统上执行任意程序。该漏洞影响 NetBSD 1.3.3 版本，攻击者需拥有本地访问权限，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。建议升级至 NetBSD 1.4 及以上版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0422"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:21.797","remediation":"升级 NetBSD 至 1.4 或更高版本，该版本已修复 mount 命令忽略 noexec 标志的问题。如无法立即升级，可在 /etc/fstab 中对敏感分区额外设置 nosuid 标志并限制本地用户登录，降低绕过执行的风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0422"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0074.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0072","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0072.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0420","title":"BSD umapfs 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"umapfs（用户映射文件系统）存在权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可通过恶意构造的 mount_umap 程序修改自身用户标识符（UID），从而绕过系统权限检查获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响使用 umapfs 的 UNIX 系统，攻击者需拥有本地访问权限，成功利用后可完全控制受影响系统，危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0420"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:21.550","remediation":"立即移除 mount_umap 程序的 setuid-root 权限（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/mount_umap），如不使用 umapfs 文件系统可直接卸载该组件。联系操作系统厂商确认是否有对应安全补丁，升级到已修复 umapfs 漏洞的版本。在不影响业务的前提下，禁用 umapfs 内核模块支持以防止恶意加载。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0420"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0072.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0073","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0073.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0421","title":"Slackware Linux 安装后重启root账户未授权登录漏洞","description":"Linux Slackware 3.6 系统在安装后首次重启过程中存在身份认证绕过漏洞。远程攻击者可在系统启动阶段利用 root 账号无需密码直接登录，从而获得系统最高权限。该漏洞源于安装程序在初次重启时未正确设置 root 账户密码，攻击条件简单，无需任何身份凭证即可完全控制目标系统。影响范围包括 Slackware 3.6 及可能的相关版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0421"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-03-17","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"安装完成后首次重启前，务必使用 passwd root 命令为 root 账户设置强密码。升级到 Slackware Linux 3.6 以上版本，新版本在安装流程中强制要求设置 root 密码。如无法升级，可在 /etc/inittab 中配置单用户模式需要密码认证，并检查 /etc/shadow 确保 root 密码字段非空。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/981","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/338"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0073.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0621","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0621.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0385","title":"Microsoft Exchange Server 5.5 LDAP Bind 函数缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Microsoft Exchange Server 5.5 目录服务的 LDAP Bind 函数存在未检查的缓冲区，远程攻击者可发送特制的畸形 Bind 请求导致缓冲区溢出，造成 Exchange 目录服务崩溃（拒绝服务），或在特定条件下通过经典缓冲区溢出技术执行任意代码。攻击无法意外触发，需要主动发送恶意 LDAP 请求。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0385"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-03-16","updated":"2003-03-10","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 官方安全公告 MS99-009 提供的补丁，或禁用 Exchange 目录服务中的 LDAP 支持，或在网络防火墙上过滤发往 TCP 端口 389 的入站数据包以降低外部攻击风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T12:17:10.890517061+00:00","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-009","https://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb;en-us;221989"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0621.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0037","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0037.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0382","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 屏幕保护程序权限提升漏洞","description":"Windows NT 中的屏幕保护程序在安全上下文切换时未正确验证权限变更，导致本地攻击者可通过物理访问终端或诱导系统进入屏保状态触发该漏洞，以提升后的权限执行任意程序。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 NT 3.5.1 的多个 Service Pack 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0382"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:16.647","remediation":"建议升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本系统（Windows NT 4.0/3.5.1 已于 2004 年停止支持，不再提供安全更新）。如无法升级，可在组策略编辑器（gpedit.msc）中启用「屏幕保护程序超时锁定」策略，并将屏幕保护程序启动等待时间设为不超过 15 分钟，同时确保所有用户账户均设有强密码，限制非授权用户的本地登录权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-008","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19359","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0382.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0382","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0382.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0382.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9h86-j86m-7fx3/GHSA-9h86-j86m-7fx3.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/1999/CVE-1999-0382.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--284f3c9d-c5aa-4a6f-9d77-395fb3b2fa10.json","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0037.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1161","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1161.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1526","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10772,\"outputTokens\":19,\"totalTokens\":10791}}","description":"Macromedia Shockwave 7 的自动更新功能存在信息泄露漏洞。该功能的实现会在执行自动更新检查时，将当前用户的登录密码以及硬盘相关信息以明文或弱保护方式回传至 Macromedia 服务器，而非仅传输必要的版本标识。该漏洞影响安装并启用自动更新功能的 Macromedia Shockwave 7 用户，攻击条件为受害者正常使用软件且处于联网状态，攻击者需能够截获或访问 Macromedia 服务器侧的回传数据方可获取敏感信息。利用方式即通过监听网络流量或控制回传路径，窃取用户密码与硬盘信息，进而可能导致账号失窃与隐私泄露。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1526"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-03-11T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:37.780","remediation":"升级 Macromedia Shockwave 到修复该问题的后续版本（建议 8.0 及以上），并在无法升级时通过 Shockwave 设置或注册表项关闭自动更新功能，避免软件在后台将用户密码与硬盘信息回传至 Macromedia 服务器；同时可在网络出口防火墙限制客户端对 macromedia.com 自动更新域名的访问作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/12842","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1931","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1ce36d0de2f3ddd1d56c222c398df994c8c331b1/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1526.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1526","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1526.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f581b54f28a314b57ac171b83d3b2d21db7414a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1526.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/11845a9fe6e6b4d82150d9fd8a4257b88a244a45/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3fq5-p5h6-7xvf/GHSA-3fq5-p5h6-7xvf.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87972/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1526.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000573.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1161.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0064","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0064.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0416","title":"Cisco 700系列路由器 Telnet TCP连接拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Cisco 7xx 系列路由器 Telnet 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标路由器的 Telnet 端口（默认 23/TCP）建立 TCP 连接，触发路由器系统重新加载，导致设备暂时不可用。该漏洞影响 Cisco 7xx 系列路由器设备，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。受影响的 Cisco 7xx 设备因无法正确处理 Telnet 端口上的 TCP 连接请求，导致设备崩溃重启，造成网络服务中断。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0416"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-03-11T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:21.073","remediation":"建议升级 Cisco 7xx 系列路由器至最新固件版本（如 IOS 11.3(5) 或更高），并在路由器上配置访问控制列表（ACL）限制 Telnet 端口的源 IP 范围，仅允许受信任的管理主机连接。如业务允许，建议禁用 Telnet 服务，改用 SSH 进行远程管理。对于已停产的 7xx 系列设备，建议尽快迁移至受支持的 Cisco 路由器型号。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/j-034.shtml","http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/770/7xxconn-pub.shtml","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19919","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0416.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0416.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0416","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0416.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0416.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p3w3-x7jr-4c3v/GHSA-p3w3-x7jr-4c3v.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0416.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0064.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0062","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0062.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0415","title":"Cisco 7xx系列路由器HTTP服务默认开启漏洞","description":"Cisco 7xx 系列路由器（3.2 至 4.2 版本）的 HTTP 服务器默认开启，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过 HTTP 接口访问路由器管理页面，进而修改路由器配置，造成网络服务中断或流量劫持。该漏洞影响 Cisco 700 系列路由器，攻击者只需知道路由器 IP 地址即可利用，危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0415"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-11T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:20.933","remediation":"升级 Cisco 7xx 系列路由器 IOS 至 4.2 以上版本，或通过命令行执行 `no http-server` 禁用 HTTP 管理服务，并在访问控制列表中限制仅允许可信管理 IP 访问路由器管理端口。若无法升级，建议在边界防火墙上阻断对路由器 TCP 80 端口的公网访问。Cisco 已在后续版本中将 HTTP 服务默认关闭。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/j-034.shtml","http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/770/7xxconn-pub.shtml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0415.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0415.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0415","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0415.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0415.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gx7p-m72r-4gq2/GHSA-gx7p-m72r-4gq2.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82498/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0415.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0062.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0065","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0065.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0417","title":"Sun Solaris 7.0 procfs 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 7.0 的 procfs（进程文件系统）存在拒绝服务漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 /proc 文件系统发送特制的请求或操作，触发系统内核崩溃或资源耗尽，导致目标系统不可用。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 7.0 版本，需本地用户身份才能利用，攻击复杂度较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0417"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-03-09","updated":"1999-03-09","remediation":"立即安装 Sun（现 Oracle）针对 Solaris 7 64-bit 系统发布的 procfs 补丁（Solaris 7 推荐补丁集 106541-xx，含 procfs 修复）。若无法升级系统，可将 /proc 文件系统挂载选项设置为 nosuid 并限制非 root 用户对 /proc 的访问权限，以缓解本地拒绝服务攻击。建议将已 EOL 的 Solaris 7 升级至受支持的 Oracle Solaris 11 或更新版本，从根本上解决此问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19326","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0417.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0417","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0417.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0417.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9pc9-mc38-6cmq/GHSA-9pc9-mc38-6cmq.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0417.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--f71e3200-5b60-40de-a215-2cc104f46dcc.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0065.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0065.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0065.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1190","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1190.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1567","title":"Seapine TestTrack 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Seapine TestTrack 服务器存在拒绝服务漏洞，攻击者可通过连接到端口 99 并在未发送数据的情况下立即断开连接，利用 TestTrackWeb.exe 或 ttcgi.exe 组件触发高 CPU 消耗，导致服务器拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Seapine TestTrack 系统用户，可导致系统资源耗尽，服务不可用，影响生产环境中的软件测试和缺陷管理流程。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1567"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-03-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:43.967","remediation":"建议升级 Seapine TestTrack 至厂商修复后的最新版本（请安装 2000 年之后发布的包含该缺陷修复的版本）。如无法立即升级，可在边界防火墙或 TCP 包装层限制仅允许受信任 IP 访问 TCP 99 端口，阻断未授权主机连接 TestTrackWeb.exe 与 ttcgi.exe 服务，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ntbugtraq.com/default.asp?pid=36&sid=1&A2=ind9903&L=NTBUGTRAQ&P=R1215","http://www.ntbugtraq.com/default.asp?pid=36&sid=1&A2=ind9906&L=NTBUGTRAQ&P=R1680","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1948","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/35cd604fbbf2927fb6acbcd700e81d36cd6dec11/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1567.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1567","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-1567.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/3a7f9488e77673498ec37285be0a165ad71720f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1567.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2a2be81fd4b47dc35d815a995b6429bd116a3b84/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h859-3f7w-cgmj/GHSA-h859-3f7w-cgmj.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87919/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1567.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--35bd3fbe-6241-4684-9a94-736544b9b995.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1190.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1087","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1087.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1371","title":"Sun Solaris 2.6/7 /usr/bin/write 本地缓冲区溢出权限提升漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.6 和 2.7 系统中 /usr/bin/write 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该命令以 setuid root 权限运行，用于向其他用户的终端发送消息，但在处理终端名称参数时未对输入长度进行有效边界检查，导致攻击者可传入超长字符串触发栈溢出。本地低权限用户可利用此漏洞覆盖返回地址并执行任意代码，从而获得 root 权限并完全控制系统。受影响版本包括 Solaris 2.6 和 Solaris 7，CVSS 评分为 7.2，危害等级为高。攻击者需先在目标系统上拥有本地访问权限，方可构造恶意终端名称参数利用该溢出。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1371"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-03-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:17.847","remediation":"建议将 Solaris 2.6 升级至补丁 105790-08 及以上，Solaris 7 升级至 106121-08 及以上（通过 SunSolve 或 patchadd 命令安装）。无法立即打补丁前，可用 chmod u-s /usr/bin/write 移除 setuid 位作为临时缓解，并限制非授权本地用户登录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92100752221493&w=2","http://www.securiteam.com/exploits/5ZP0O1P35O.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7546","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/256","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e244b55bdff85b2483c0e6a7cecd12f8bee0df6e/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1371.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1087.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1023","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1023.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1254","title":"Microsoft Windows 95/98/NT 4.0 ICMP 重定向消息 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 95/98/NT 4.0 操作系统存在 ICMP 重定向消息欺骗漏洞。远程攻击者可通过伪造路由器发送的 ICMP 重定向报文，诱使目标系统修改路由表条目，将网络流量导向无效或恶意路径，导致目标系统无法正常访问网络资源，形成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows 95、98 及 NT 4.0 版本，无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。微软至今未发布官方补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1254"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:02.813","remediation":"由于 Windows 95/98/NT 4.0 均已停止支持且无官方补丁，建议立即升级至受支持的 Windows 版本（如 Windows 10/11）。如无法升级，可在防火墙或路由器上过滤入站 ICMP 重定向报文（类型 5），或在主机上禁用 ICMP 路由发现功能（将 EnableICMPRedirect 注册表值设为 0）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92099515709467&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1947","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1254.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1254","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1254.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1254.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-72gc-hjc8-g277/GHSA-72gc-hjc8-g277.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87822/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1254.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000568.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1023.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0069","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0069.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0418","title":"Sendmail SMTP 服务拒绝服务漏洞","description":"该漏洞存在于 SMTP 服务器（如 Sendmail）中，远程攻击者可在同一连接中发送大量 RCPT TO 命令，耗尽服务器资源导致拒绝服务。攻击无需身份认证，仅需能连接目标 SMTP 端口（通常为 25/TCP）。影响运行 Sendmail 等 SMTP 软件的主机，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0418"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-03-08","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.9.0 或更高版本，该版本引入了连接限制机制。在 sendmail.cf 中设置 MaxRecipientsPerMessage=N（如 100）限制单次 SMTP 连接的 RCPT TO 数量。同时配置 access 文件拒绝来源异常的发件 IP，或在 MTA 层面启用 rate limiting 限制同一来源的并发连接数。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92100018214316&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0069.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0057","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0057.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0411","title":"SCO OpenServer Enterprise System 启动脚本符号链接攻击本地提权漏洞","description":"SCO OpenServer Enterprise System 5.0.4p 版本的多个启动脚本（包括 S84rpcinit、S95nis、S85tcp、S89nfs）存在符号链接攻击漏洞。本地攻击者可通过创建恶意符号链接，利用系统启动脚本在处理临时文件时的权限提升缺陷，在脚本以 root 权限执行时覆盖或篡改系统关键文件，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SCO OpenServer Enterprise System 5.0.4p 及可能的相关版本，需要本地访问权限方能利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0411"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-03-07","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:20.400","remediation":"建议升级至 SCO OpenServer 5.0.5 及以上版本（若厂商已发布补丁）；由于 SCO OpenServer 已停止维护，建议迁移至受支持的操作系统。临时缓解措施：修改受影响启动脚本（S84rpcinit、S95nis、S85tcp、S89nfs）中临时文件的创建方式，使用 mktemp 替代直接写入 /tmp 目录，并将脚本文件权限设置为 root 可写（chmod 700），同时定期审计 /tmp 目录中的异常符号链接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0411","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0411"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0057.toml"}]